TIVision 
Framework of cpp-sources for image processing labs at Haagse Hogeschool Rijswijk
Opleiding Technische Informatica (Department of Computer Science).

make: for building all the sources in the TIVision directory.
make clean: removing the builts
./go running the software   (a file image1.pgm-file, 640x480, 8bit should be present)
./stop closing all the eog and xgraph windows

dependend on:
- eog (for viewing the pgm-files)
- xgraph (for diagrams)
- libdc1394v2.0 (for cam reading)

